# English-Only Project Content

- Write project files, comments, documentation, UI text, API messages, tests, and examples in English.
- Do not introduce Chinese text or other non-English prose into the repository unless the user explicitly asks for localized content.
- If existing non-English text is touched, translate it to English as part of the change.
